title: South Africa 30 Year bond-Yield
description: South Africa 30 Year Bond Yield was 11.41 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Africa 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 14.25 in March of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Africa 30Y.
